page.title: 20Changes in the area
page.content: People in the area around Launceston say that it has changed a great deal in the past years but the outlying districts are still very isolated.Many of the people here have never moved away from Cornwall and are rightly proud of being Cornish.Most of the class 3H at Launceston College who have entered this data are Cornish. They are Abigail Bates,Claire Cable Tim Cedar,Helen Davey,Graham Dumper, Carol Edwards,Julian Elliott,Mark Harris,Neil Heard,Guy Hopkins,Andrew Jones,Mark Kinvig,Stephen Lankston, Philip Locke,Helen Mills,Joanne Norman,Tessa Osborne,Lisa Parnell, Helen Partridge,Debbie Peel,Adrian Retallack,Lee Smale,Claire Strudwick,Andrew Voyzey,Tanya Wenden, Linda Yeo,Alistair Smith.
